    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 specifies a single quasi-static load rate and the quantitative validation metrics (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%) are satisfied for all QoIs across both test laboratories. Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium assurance level submission. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; the digital signature workflow is pending and will be completed prior to regulatory submission.",
